## Store Credits [/v1/my/payment-methods/store-credits]

Customer's Store Credits.

### List [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (StoreCreditsWithTotals)

### View [GET /v1/my/payment-methods/store-credits/{id}]

+ Parameters
  + id: 1 (required, number) - Store Credit ID
+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Attributes (StoreCredit)

### List Transactions [GET /v1/my/payment-methods/store-credits/transactions]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Attributes (StoreCreditAdjustments)

### View Totals [GET /v1/my/payment-methods/store-credits/totals]

+ Response 200 (application/json)
  + Attributes (StoreCreditTotals)
